 <h1>Ore Dictionary Filter</h1>
 <h3>Source</h3>
 <text pwt="true"><style color="0xaaaaaa" italic="true" pwt="true">Note: this page is ported from MCMOD's GTCEu wiki.<br/>Author: <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/58396/">Sofuras</style><br/></style></text>
